      "rationale": "Three-mesh GCI study completed at 3 of 5 operating points; the two highest-speed conditions were assessed only on two mesh levels due to computational cost. GCI values at assessed points were below 8 %, but extrapolation uncertainty at the remaining points is unquantified."
